			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load up CTY_Main_A\r\nGo to -1935; -7; 206\r\nUse Debug Book to get runepowder bomb\r\n(Set quest flags and options > Act 3 Low > 10. Steel Watch Foundry > 5. Get Runepowder Bomb\r\nClick Neural Switchboard > 3. Carefully place the Rune Bomb Powder) \r\nwait for the explosion cinematic to finish\r\nobserve the cutscene.\r\nChoose to side with Wulbren against the Gondians, and kill them.\r\nClick on Wulbren to trigger this dialog"
				},
